data.description: Nestled at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, this custom built home sits on over 2 wooded acres of prime deep water! Just a few miles from shopping and the inter­state, it still feels very private. It boasts a dock with lift, Over 5,000 sq. ft of living space, a floor plan that is open, airy and great for entertaining! It features a spacious screened in porch and huge deck with hot tub! Inside has an open foyer, living room, dining room, huge gourmet kitchen with a center island and produce sink, breakfast bar, granite counters, upgraded appliances and custom stonework over the oven. Open to the very large great room that features a cus­tom stone face fireplace. 1st floor bedroom and full bath, the 2nd floor Master must be seen to be believed; it has a sitting area, large walk in closet and a master bath that features a jetted tub, separate shower along with a hand painted mural! If you are looking for a waterfront home and like to enter­tain, this just might be the house of your dreams!
